    tmp = (v1 * ((v1 + 0.35 * tmp + 0.01) * 0.93))
    v1 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.05 + tmp + 0.14)) / (tmp * wp.cos(v0 + 0.77)))
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.59 * v1 + 0.96) - (v1 + 0.66 / v0 + 0.86)))

    data[tid] = v0
